@node Geschichte
@{b}@{fg shine}History:
--------@{fg text}@{ub}

  BETA 0.1   : - First public release.
  (01.09.98)

  BETA 0.1.1 : - Superplay.library is not needed to run Cybermagic.
  (07.09.98)   - Fixed the CX_POPKEY and CX_POPUP bug.
               - Control Cybermagic with Exchange.
               - Translated Installer Script.

  BETA 0.2   : - Improved control with Exchange.
  (20.09.98)   - Input to the Stringfields in the BILD/TON order are
                 now possible.
               - Added a new order (Player).
               - New module "Moire" integrated.
               - Wizard.library in the version 40.101 integrated.
               - German Amigaguide file integrated.

  BETA 0.3.0 : - AREXX Port integrated.
  (10.10.98)   - DeliTracker2 support with ARexx.
               - Hotkey to start the blanker modul.
               - Menubar.
               - Fixed CyberGuard/Enforcer hits.

  BETA 0.3.1 : - ClickToFront function for the middle mousekey.
  (20.11.98)   - Random function for Blanker and Sound moduls.
               - English AmigaGuide file integrated.
               - Fixed a bug in the DeliTracker support.

  BETA 0.3.2 : - Bugfixed the ClickToFront function.
  (20.01.99)   - HippoPlayer support with ARexx.
               - New module "Pendulum".
               - InstallerFX support.

  BETA 0.4.0 : - Glow icon design.
  (25.07.99)   - New look for the file lister.
               - Little bug fixing.
               - Warp3D and DPMS modules added.

  V0.4.1     : - DPMS function are now included in Cybermagic.
  (16.10.99)

  V0.5.0     : - WarpOS port of the 3D module.
  (17.12.99)   - New 3D module "Morph".
               - AmigaOS3.5 Installer script.

  V0.5.1     : - New 3D module "In&Out"
  (23.12.99)


@endnode

